commit.message:
Add <SearchConcept/> to render search queries and results (related concepts,
classes, and lectures)
Add <SmallerVideoCard/> to replace <VideoVard/> on related lectures tab
Add ability to click on a related lecture link and jump to it
Fix props data formats for passing through classes, lectures, and slides
Add <ClassesManager/> to act as logic/props layer between <App/> and <ViewLecturesPage/>
Remove <SlideViewCondensed/> and port code over to <SlideView/> to reduce redundancy
Create <SlideViewCondensed/> for rendering a Slide and its related content
Create <ViewLecturesPage/> to view lecture videos for a given class

Add <Navbar/> as a navbar for the page. Add Colors.css for managing color
themes across the app
Initial commit from Create React App
